videos.description: Georgia's Parker attempts to keep the ball in-bounds, accidentally hits South Carolina's Thornwell in the face..
videos.headline: Juwan Parker pass hits  Sindarius Thornwell in the face

videos.description: When South Carolina's Chris Silver turns over the ball, Georgia's J.J. Frazier makes the steal and drives to the hoop for the lay in.
videos.headline: Georgia's Frazier turns defense into offense

videos.description: J.J. Frazier steal cues the Bulldog break, he feeds it to Juwan Parker, who absorbs the contact and finishes at the rim
videos.headline: Georgia's Parker absorbs the contact and finishes at the rim

videos.description: S. Thornwell slashes to the basket and lays it in.
videos.headline: Sindarius Thornwell carves through the Bulldogs D for two

videos.description: J. Harris made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by J. Frazier.
videos.headline: J.J. Frazier threads incredible pass to Jordan Harris who nails the three.

videos.description: Georgia's Jordan Harris dishes a great push pass to Derek Ogbeide, who dunks with authority.
videos.headline: Georgia's Harris finds Ogbeide for the slam dunk

videos.description: Justin McKie rips the ball clean and finds S. Thornwell down court for the big triple
videos.headline: Suffocating Gamecocks D leads to Sindarius Thornwell triple

videos.description: P. Dozier draws contact and floats it in. South Carolina leads by nine
videos.headline: PJ Dozier powers through traffic and floats it in

videos.description: Dalen Cuff and Beth Mowen sit down with South Carolina Coach Frank Martin.
videos.headline: Postgame interview with South Carolina Coach Frank Martin who discusses how great guard play helped power the Gamecocks to victory

videos.description: No. 19 South Carolina improves to 9-1 in conference play with a 77-75 victory over Georgia.
videos.headline: South Carolina holds off Georgia
